lead_paragraph: British track sprinter Jess Varnish will not appeal against her non-selection for the Rio Olympics but launched a fierce criticism of British Cycling on Wednesday.

headline.print_headline: Varnish Won't Appeal Olympic Snub, Criticizes British Cycling
